Version 0.1.8 (dan)
	* Allow caller to set name of each data source via add_cdbs()
	* Allow caller to get last_updated
	* Add back median test.
	* Added CircularDB::Statistics class and shortcuts.
	* Implement aggregation for aggregated cdbs.

Version 0.1.7 (dan)
	* Handle single CircularDB::Storage case when graphing.
	* Deal with IO or File objects
	* Add driver_end_time to Aggregate.
	* Add graph method to CircularDB::Storage.
	* Additional debugging for Aggregate.
	* More tweaks - use tmpfile for sending back return data.

Version 0.1.6 (dan)
	* New Makefile.am - PLATFORM-184

Version 0.1.5 (dan)
	* Move to Makefile.am

Version 0.1.4 (dan)
	* Fix runtime deps

Version 0.1.3 (dan)
	* Add wrappers for aggregation functions.
	* Update for new cdb_read_records() API.
	* Add tests for aggregation.
	* Fix memory leak in the read_records routines.

Version 0.1.2 (dan)
	* Pass in flags & mode for file open.
	* Raise exceptions to the Ruby layer.
	* Graphing updates. Silence a bunch of warnings.

Version 0.1.1 (dan)
	* Minor logic cleanups. Remove GSL check until kevin installs it.
	* Add prettier unit display.
	* Add some small utilities. Fix validation bug.

Version 0.1.0 (dan)
	* First commit

